{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/Django/Deploying-with-EC2-Nginx-Gunicorn-Django","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"a0b9cc22-e153-5eed-840a-cf75dfb07933","html":"<h1 id=\"installing-the-packages-from-the-ubuntu-repositories우분투-셋팅\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#installing-the-packages-from-the-ubuntu-repositories%EC%9A%B0%EB%B6%84%ED%88%AC-%EC%85%8B%ED%8C%85\" aria-label=\"installing the packages from the ubuntu repositories우분투 셋팅 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Installing the Packages from the Ubuntu Repositories(우분투 셋팅)</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">sudo apt <span class=\"token keyword\">update</span>\nsudo apt install python3<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>pip python3<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>dev libpq<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>dev nginx libmysqlclient<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>dev</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"creating-a-python-virtual-environment-for-your-project가상환경-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#creating-a-python-virtual-environment-for-your-project%EA%B0%80%EC%83%81%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"creating a python virtual environment for your project가상환경 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Creating a Python Virtual Environment for your Project(가상환경 생성)</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">sudo <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>H pip3 install <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>upgrade pip\nsudo <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>H pip3 install virtualenv\nvirtualenv <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>가상환경 이름<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>             # 생성\n<span class=\"token keyword\">source</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>가상환경 이름<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token builtin\">bin</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>activate    # 활성화\npip install django gunicorn        # gunicorn 설치</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"creating-and-configuring-a-new-django-projectdjango-프로젝트-생성-및-구성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#creating-and-configuring-a-new-django-projectdjango-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1-%EB%B0%8F-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"creating and configuring a new django projectdjango 프로젝트 생성 및 구성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Creating and Configuring a New Django Project(Django 프로젝트 생성 및 구성)</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">git clone <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>github 주소<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"allowed_hosts-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#allowed_hosts-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"allowed_hosts 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ALLOWED_HOSTS 설정</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">ALLOWED_HOSTS <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'your_server_domain_or_IP'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'second_domain_or_IP'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'localhost'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"migrate\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#migrate\" aria-label=\"migrate permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>migrate</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\"><span class=\"token keyword\">python</span> manage<span class=\"token operator\">.</span><span class=\"token keyword\">py</span> migrate</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"8000-port-허용\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#8000-port-%ED%97%88%EC%9A%A9\" aria-label=\"8000 port 허용 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>8000 port 허용</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">sudo ufw allow <span class=\"token number\">8000</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"앱이-나오는지-확인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%95%B1%EC%9D%B4-%EB%82%98%EC%98%A4%EB%8A%94%EC%A7%80-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"앱이 나오는지 확인 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>앱이 나오는지 확인</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://server_domain_or_IP:8000\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://server_domain_or_IP:8000</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"gunicorn\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gunicorn\" aria-label=\"gunicorn permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gunicorn</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">gunicorn <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>bind <span class=\"token number\">0.0</span><span class=\"token operator\">.</span><span class=\"token number\">0.0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">8000</span> myproject<span class=\"token operator\">.</span>wsgi</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"가상환경-비활성화\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%80%EC%83%81%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD-%EB%B9%84%ED%99%9C%EC%84%B1%ED%99%94\" aria-label=\"가상환경 비활성화 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>가상환경 비활성화</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">deactivate</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"creating-systemd-socket-and-service-files-for-gunicorngunicorn-용-systemd-소켓-및-서비스-파일-만들기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#creating-systemd-socket-and-service-files-for-gunicorngunicorn-%EC%9A%A9-systemd-%EC%86%8C%EC%BC%93-%EB%B0%8F-%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4-%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"creating systemd socket and service files for gunicorngunicorn 용 systemd 소켓 및 서비스 파일 만들기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Creating systemd Socket and Service Files for Gunicorn(Gunicorn 용 systemd 소켓 및 서비스 파일 만들기)</h1>\n<h3 id=\"gunicornsocket\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gunicornsocket\" aria-label=\"gunicornsocket permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gunicorn.socket</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>내부 [Unit]에서 소켓을 설명하는 [Socket]섹션, 소켓 위치를 정의하는 [Install]섹션, 소켓이 적시에 생성되었는지 확인 하는 섹션을 생성</li>\n<li>sudo 권한이 있는 Gunicorn용 시스템 소켓 파일을 만들고 여는 것으로 시작</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">sudo <span class=\"token keyword\">vi</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>etc<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>systemd<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>system<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>gunicorn<span class=\"token operator\">.</span>socket</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>Unit<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\nDescription<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>gunicorn socket\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>Socket<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\nListenStream<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>run<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>gunicorn<span class=\"token operator\">.</span>sock\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>Install<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\nWantedBy<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>sockets<span class=\"token operator\">.</span>target</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"gunicornservice\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gunicornservice\" aria-label=\"gunicornservice permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gunicorn.service</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>sudo 텍스트 편집기에서 권한이 있는 Gunicorn에 대한 systemd 서비스 파일 생성 </li>\n<li>서비스 파일 이름은 확장자를 제외하고 소켓 파일 이름과 일치해야 함</li>\n<li>서비스는 소켓 파일의 소켓에 의존하기 때문에 Requires해당 관계를 나타내는 지시문을 포함해야 함</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">sudo <span class=\"token keyword\">vi</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>etc<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>systemd<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>system<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>gunicorn<span class=\"token operator\">.</span>service</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>Unit<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\nDescription<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>gunicorn daemon\nRequires<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>gunicorn<span class=\"token operator\">.</span>socket\nAfter<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>network<span class=\"token operator\">.</span>target\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>Service<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\nUser<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>ubuntu\nGroup<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>www<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>data\nWorkingDirectory<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>home<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>ubuntu<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>myprojectdir\nExecStart<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>home<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>ubuntu<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>myprojectdir<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>myprojectenv<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token builtin\">bin</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>gunicorn \\\n          <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>access<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>logfile <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> \\\n          <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>workers <span class=\"token number\">3</span> \\\n          <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>bind unix<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>run<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>gunicorn<span class=\"token operator\">.</span>sock \\\n          myproject<span class=\"token operator\">.</span>wsgi<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>application\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>Install<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\nWantedBy<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>multi<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>user<span class=\"token operator\">.</span>target</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"socket-시작-및-활성화-상태-확인active-active-running\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#socket-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91-%EB%B0%8F-%ED%99%9C%EC%84%B1%ED%99%94-%EC%83%81%ED%83%9C-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8active-active-running\" aria-label=\"socket 시작 및 활성화 상태 확인active active running permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>socket 시작 및 활성화, 상태 확인(Active: active (running))</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">sudo systemctl start gunicorn<span class=\"token operator\">.</span>socket\nsudo systemctl enable gunicorn<span class=\"token operator\">.</span>socket</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"terminal\"><pre class=\"language-terminal\"><code class=\"language-terminal\">$ sudo systemctl status gunicorn.socket\nFailed to dump process list, ignoring: No such file or directory\n● gunicorn.socket - gunicorn socket\n   Loaded: loaded (/etc/systemd/system/gunicorn.socket; enabled; vendor preset: enabled)\n   Active: active (running) since Fri 2020-08-07 08:00:53 UTC; 1h 23min ago\n   Listen: /run/gunicorn.sock (Stream)\n   CGroup: /system.slice/gunicorn.socket\n\nAug 07 08:00:53 ip-172-31-36-173 systemd[1]: Closed gunicorn socket.\nAug 07 08:00:53 ip-172-31-36-173 systemd[1]: Stopping gunicorn socket.\nAug 07 08:00:53 ip-172-31-36-173 systemd[1]: Listening on gunicorn socket.</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"gunicorn-gunicornsocket-로그-보기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gunicorn-gunicornsocket-%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8-%EB%B3%B4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"gunicorn gunicornsocket 로그 보기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gunicorn, gunicorn.socket 로그 보기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">sudo journalctl <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token keyword\">u</span> gunicorn\nsudo journalctl <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token keyword\">u</span> gunicorn<span class=\"token operator\">.</span>socket</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"gunicorn-프로세스-재시작\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gunicorn-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%84%B8%EC%8A%A4-%EC%9E%AC%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91\" aria-label=\"gunicorn 프로세스 재시작 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Gunicorn 프로세스 재시작</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">sudo systemctl daemon<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>reload\nsudo systemctl restart gunicorn</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"configure-nginx-to-proxy-pass-to-gunicorngunicorn에-프록시-패스로-nginx-구성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#configure-nginx-to-proxy-pass-to-gunicorngunicorn%EC%97%90-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9D%EC%8B%9C-%ED%8C%A8%EC%8A%A4%EB%A1%9C-nginx-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"configure nginx to proxy pass to gunicorngunicorn에 프록시 패스로 nginx 구성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Configure Nginx to Proxy Pass to Gunicorn(Gunicorn에 프록시 패스로 Nginx 구성)</h1>\n<h3 id=\"sites-available\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#sites-available\" aria-label=\"sites available permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>sites-available</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">sudo <span class=\"token keyword\">vi</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>etc<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>nginx<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>sites<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>available<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>myproject</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">server <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    listen <span class=\"token number\">80</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    server_name server_domain_or_IP<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    location <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>favicon<span class=\"token operator\">.</span>ico <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> access_log off<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> log_not_found off<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    location <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>static<span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        root <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>home<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>ubuntu<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>myprojectdir<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    location <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token builtin\">include</span> proxy_params<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        proxy_pass http<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>unix<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>run<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>gunicorn<span class=\"token operator\">.</span>sock<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">sudo <span class=\"token keyword\">ln</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>s <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>etc<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>nginx<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>sites<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>available<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>myproject <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>etc<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>nginx<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>sites<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>enabled</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"sites-enabled-에-default-제거\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#sites-enabled-%EC%97%90-default-%EC%A0%9C%EA%B1%B0\" aria-label=\"sites enabled 에 default 제거 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>sites-enabled 에 default 제거</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">sudo rm <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>etc<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>nginx<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>sites<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>enabled<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>default</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"nginx-재시작\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#nginx-%EC%9E%AC%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91\" aria-label=\"nginx 재시작 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>nginx 재시작</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">sudo nginx <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token keyword\">t</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> sudo systemctl restart nginx</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"nginx-에러-로그-보기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#nginx-%EC%97%90%EB%9F%AC-%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8-%EB%B3%B4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"nginx 에러 로그 보기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>nginx 에러 로그 보기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">sudo tail <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>F <span class=\"token operator\">/</span>var<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>log<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>nginx<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>error<span class=\"token operator\">.</span>log</code></pre></div>\n<h1 id=\"위에서-허용했던-8000-port-제거--포트-80의-일반-트래픽에-방화벽을-열기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9C%84%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%ED%97%88%EC%9A%A9%ED%96%88%EB%8D%98-8000-port-%EC%A0%9C%EA%B1%B0--%ED%8F%AC%ED%8A%B8-80%EC%9D%98-%EC%9D%BC%EB%B0%98-%ED%8A%B8%EB%9E%98%ED%94%BD%EC%97%90-%EB%B0%A9%ED%99%94%EB%B2%BD%EC%9D%84-%EC%97%B4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"위에서 허용했던 8000 port 제거  포트 80의 일반 트래픽에 방화벽을 열기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>위에서 허용했던 8000 port 제거 &#x26; 포트 80의 일반 트래픽에 방화벽을 열기</h1>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vim\"><pre class=\"language-vim\"><code class=\"language-vim\">sudo ufw <span class=\"token keyword\">delete</span> allow <span class=\"token number\">8000</span>\nsudo ufw allow <span class=\"token string\">'Nginx Full'</span></code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/Django/Deploying-with-EC2-Nginx-Gunicorn-Django","tagSlugs":["/tag/deploying-with-ec-2-nginx-gunicorn-django/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-08-07","description":"EC2, Nginx, Gunicorn, Django로 배포하기","tags":["Deploying-with-EC2-Nginx-Gunicorn-Django"],"title":"Deploying with EC2, Nginx, Gunicorn, Django","socialImage":""}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/Django/Deploying-with-EC2-Nginx-Gunicorn-Django"}}}